        <pre class="group relative bg-bg rounded-lg border border-border p-3 text-xs"><code class="text-accent font-mono">Authorization: Bearer &lt;your-rrf-token&gt;</code></pre>
      </div>
      <p class="text-xs text-text-muted">
        To obtain a registration token, use <code class="font-mono text-accent">castor rrf register</code> (OpenCastor) or contact the RRF directly.
        Tokens are tied to an RRN and scoped to that robot's records. Tokens have a maximum TTL of 1 year and must be rotated before expiry.
      </p>
